OL,3,CSarah Ferguson stripped of Freedom of
OL,4,CYork title in unanimous council debate
OL,6,FSarah Ferguson has been stripped of
OL,7,Fher Freedom of the City of York title
OL,8,Fover her ties to sex offender Jeffrey
OL,9,FEpstein.
OL,11,FThe former Duchess of York was given
OL,12,Fthe title as a wedding gift while
OL,13,Fmarried to Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor,
OL,14,Fformerly Prince Andrew, who has
OL,15,Falready seen his Freedom of the City
OL,16,Frescinded over his connections to the
OL,17,Fpaedophile financier.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
