OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774789868
OL,3,CSarah Ferguson stripped of Freedom of
OL,4,CYork title in unanimous council debate
OL,6,FIn a brief debate on Thursday evening
OL,7,Fat York's Guildhall, councillors voted
OL,8,Funanimously to remove the title
OL,9,Fbestowed back in 1987.
OL,11,FIt follows the unearthing of emails
OL,12,Fsent by the former Duchess to Epstein
OL,13,Fin 2011, three years after his 2008
OL,14,Fconviction for soliciting prostitution
OL,15,Ffrom a minor, calling him a
OL,16,F"steadfast, generous and supreme
OL,17,Ffriend" to her family.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
