OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774789868
OL,3,CSarah Ferguson stripped of Freedom of
OL,4,CYork title in unanimous council debate
OL,6,FFreedom of the City titles are granted
OL,7,Fby councils in acknowledgment of a
OL,8,Ffigure's services to its people, such
OL,9,Fas acts of bravery or a lifetime's
OL,10,Fpublic service.
OL,12,FAddressing councillors ahead of
OL,13,FThursday's meeting, Gwen Swinburn
OL,14,Fsaid, "it is the absolute minimum you
OL,15,Fshould be doing".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
