PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774789868
OL,3,CSarah Ferguson stripped of Freedom of
OL,4,CYork title in unanimous council debate
OL,6,FShe told the meeting: "It chips away
OL,7,Fat reputation of this city, quietly,
OL,8,Frepeatedly, by a thousand cuts. If you
OL,9,Fremove the freedom tonight, you remove
OL,10,Fjust one of those cuts, but leave the
OL,11,Frest.
OL,13,F"The name of York carries history, it
OL,14,Fcarries weight and standing. It should
OL,15,Fnot be carried in a way that
OL,16,Fdiminishes it."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
