OL,3,CSarah Ferguson stripped of Freedom of
OL,4,CYork title in unanimous council debate
OL,6,FA statement afterwards issued by the
OL,7,FLeader of City of York Council, Cllr
OL,8,FJane Douglas, said that liaising with
OL,9,Fknown criminals like Epstein fell
OL,10,F"well short" of expectations for those
OL,11,Fbearing the title.
OL,13,FCllr Douglas said: "Honorary Freedom
OL,14,Fis bestowed only on persons of
OL,15,Fdistinction and those having given
OL,16,Feminent services to the City of York.
OL,26,@uD@TOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
