OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774789868
OL,3,CSarah Ferguson stripped of Freedom of
OL,4,CYork title in unanimous council debate
OL,6,F"As the people of York would expect,
OL,7,Fholding this status requires upholding
OL,8,Fthe values and behaviours consistent
OL,9,Fwith such an honour. Those who
OL,10,Fcontinued to associate with Epstein
OL,11,Fafter his crimes became widely known
OL,12,Ffall well short of these expectations."
OL,14,FShe added: "City of York councillors
OL,15,Fconsidered these issues this evening
OL,16,Fand agreed that removing the honour
OL,17,Ffrom Sarah Ferguson was appropriate.
OL,18,FThis was the right decision to take to
OL,19,Fmaintain the integrity and standing of
OL,20,Fthis important York honour."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@gO]vD@LOU|D@\O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
