OL,3,CSarah Ferguson stripped of Freedom of
OL,4,CYork title in unanimous council debate
OL,6,FYork Central MP Rachel Maskell (Lab)
OL,7,Ftold ITV: "Ultimately, Freedom of the
OL,8,FCity is a privilege who have made a
OL,9,Fsignificant contribution to our city.
OL,10,FOf course the associations that Sarah
OL,11,FFerguson has had with Jeffrey Epstein
OL,12,Feven after knowing that he assaulted a
OL,13,Fchild, I have to say is really
OL,14,Fabhorrent.
OL,16,F"I think it's the right decision of
OL,17,Fthe council to move this motion
OL,18,Fforward, to strip the Freedom of the
OL,19,FCity, and I'm sure it will be welcome
OL,20,Facross the whole of York."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
